<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فِيهِ مَسَائِلُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأُولَى:</span> تَفْسِيرُ آيَةِ البَقَرَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الثَّانِيَةُ:</span> تَفْسِيرُ آيَةِ النِّسَاءِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الثَّالِثَةُ:</span> تَفْسِيرُ الجِبْتِ وَالطَّاغُوتِ، وَالفَرَقُ بَينَهُمَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الرَّابِعَةُ:</span> أَنَّ الطَّاغُوتَ قَدْ يَكُونُ مِنَ الجِنِّ وَقَدْ يَكُونُ مِنَ الإِنْسِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الخَامِسَةُ:</span> مَعْرِفَةُ السَّبْعِ المُوبِقَاتِ المَخْصُوصَاتِ بِالنَّهْيِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">السَّادِسَةُ:</span> أَنَّ السَّاحِرَ يَكْفُرُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">السَّابِعَةُ:</span> أَنَّهُ يُقْتَلُ وَلَا يُسْتَتَابُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">الثَّامِنَةُ:</span> وُجُودُ هَذَا فِي المُسْلِمِينَ عَلَى عَهْدِ عُمَرَ؛ فَكَيفَ بَعْدَهُ؟!<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>